n V Superman’ Toys & Merchandise Details Teased for Licensing Expo 2015 |publisher=Screenrant.com |date=2015-06-05 |accessdate=2015-09-24 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001031252/http://screenrant.com/batman-v-superman-movie-toys-merchandise/ |archivedate=2015-10-01 }}</ref>。

